Clone into to your pathogen bundle

Now supports setting a single char for comments, # by default.

let g:commenter_char = "#"
let g:commenter_char = '"'

Now supports moving, 1 line down by default.

let g:commenter_move_on = 1
let g:commenter_move_on = 0
let g:commenter_move_on = -1

